Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:07.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,每年在下雪前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Every year before the snow came,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸都会烧残骸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my father would burn slash piles--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,动物尸体  落下的树枝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}mounds of dead, fallen brush,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,火焰有谷仓那么高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with flames as high as the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会抬起头  顶着高温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd hold my face up to the heat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,逼自己靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and dare myself closer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像我是在朝着太阳走一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like I was walking into the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,呸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,-水和泥土  -你分析了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Water and dirt. - You analyzed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,海德伍德夫妇分析了  什么都没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Headwoods did. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,毫无意外  所以你为什么取样这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's exactly what you'd expect, so why did you sample this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面有硫酸铵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was there ammonium sulfate in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  多半是火山岩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm-hmm, it's probably volcanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:17.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,那又如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,他警告过我这个  他说你会有所保留\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He warned me about this. He said that you hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:25.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的主要战术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's your main move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:28.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说世界上有两种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said that there is two different types of people in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,一种是梦想家一种是阴谋家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's dreamers and there's schemers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:32.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,梦想家可以打造世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the dreamers can build the world up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:35.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,而阴谋家会趁机溜过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the schemers slither their way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:38.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他嗨了后话很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think that he says a lot when he's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,当时外面在下雪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was snowing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,-天空上下下来的吗  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- From the sky? - From the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mm-hmm, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:50.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,-本应不可能  但我看到了  -我们不会看到雪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It should be, but I saw it. - We don't get snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,太冷了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有高吹雪和以前的沉淀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We get blowing snow and old precip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你或许能影响到他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You might get into his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你影响不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you're not getting into mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:01:59.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,熄灯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:03.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,当艾莉克斯年龄足够大时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When Alex was old enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,她帮我用水管冲洗灰池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she helped me hose down the ash pits,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:10.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会像我爸警告我那样警告她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'd warn her like my dad warned me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,里面潜伏的高温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the heat lurking inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备像鬼魂来访一样闷烧起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}ready to smolder to life like a visit from a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:21.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在是她在雪国列车上的循环\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These are her revolutions now on Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1,034 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:44.88,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs36\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,85)}雪国列{\fsp0}车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:44.88,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第二{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"暖意渐生{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:54.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:59.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天就别去三等厢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, maybe stay out of Third today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得去帮助佩尔顿医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gotta help Dr. Pelton today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  马泰奥还在生你气  扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, Mateo is still angry with you, Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,给下面你的人一点时间冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give it some time to cool off down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,让佩尔顿去二等厢诊所工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ask Pelton to work in the Second Class clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  我不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry. I'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was thinking--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子需要名字  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this kid's gonna need a name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pretty sure that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, if it's a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得用你妈妈的名字命名怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how would you feel about naming it after your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:27.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是男孩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if it's a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,托洛茨基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Trotsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚点再谈吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,早\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,真高兴你们安顿下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to see you two landed on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是给扎拉和孩子的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's for Zarah and the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  有一个能称为家的地方很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, no, no, it's good to have a place to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:48.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很为你骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,别尬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't be weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:56.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:03.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,列车上的人状态怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's the train holding together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:04.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,比我好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,车上一半的人认为威尔福德是来杀我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Half the train thinks Wilford's here to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,另一半认为他是来从你手中解救我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The other half think he's here to save us from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们也许是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They might all be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,总人口增加了四百车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And adding 400 Tailies to the population hasn't exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,并没有降低温度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}lowered the temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:18.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚在茶室附近发生了一起袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was an assault near the Tea Room last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,-一名车尾女人受伤致残  -谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- A Tailie woman got maimed. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:24.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能去查清原委吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you find out what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我  凭什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me? On what authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是司闸员了  莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not a Brakeman anymore, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:33.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只是...  你的跟班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just... I just follow you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们解决这问题  跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, let's fix that. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -快来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What? - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗切  起来  我们来完成这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Roche, stand up. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,-现在吗  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What, now? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,贝丝·提尔  请举起右手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bess Till please raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,贝丝·提尔  我在此任命你为列车警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bess Till, I hereby pronounce you train detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  我没主动要求这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no, no, I didn't ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁会想主动收拾现在这烂摊子呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Imagine anyone asking for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,听我说  我没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me, I'm not ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他直接给你升职了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's straight up giving you a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经见过够多流血和杀戮了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've seen enough blood for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都惊魂未定  但现在由我们管事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're all shaky, but we are in charge now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们对其余乘客有责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we have a responsibility to the rest of the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你想要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得在这里审问一名战俘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we have to interrogate a POW in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能去查袭击的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so if you could get on top of this assault thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我会很感激  -警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I would really appreciate it. - Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜  刚才的仪式很动人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Congratulations, that was a really beautiful ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  贝丝·提尔警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen, Detective Bess Till.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文·麦克曼  出生地纽约水牛城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin McMann, born in Buffalo, New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,以乘客服务部学徒身份登上雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}ticketed on Snowpiercer as a hospitality apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-现在我是部门主管  -恭喜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm head of department now. - Ah, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们列车上有多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So how many people you looking after back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝回答  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna decline to answer, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们看起来有点饿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You guys looked a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们的食物系统还撑得住吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How your food systems holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:56.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你不用怕威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, you don't have to fear Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你在这里很安全  -怕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're safe up here. - Fear him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我崇拜那个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I adore the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你  你以前是安保  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I remember you. Security, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,戴着耳机走来走去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Walked around with your little earpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,在他进入房间前先确认安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cleared the room before he entered
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,有点像门卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}kind of like a doorman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:18.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,是有点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:21.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,安保  工程部  农业部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Security, engineering, agriculture--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,都只是管道系统  但乘客服务部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's all just plumbing, but Hospitality--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,乘客服务部从心出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hospitality comes from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:32.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,是一种文化  一种爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a culture. It's a kind of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:34.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会来救我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要说的就这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all I'm gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这是真的吗  -真鸡肉  对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is that real? - Real chicken, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,真醋  真辣椒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's real vinegar, real cayenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟家乡一样的水牛城风味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's Buffalo style just like home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们说说那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell us about the big guy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,脸像棒球手套一样厚的大块头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with a baseball mitt for a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么不受极寒影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why wasn't he affected by the cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,他被增强了耐寒性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was augmented for cold resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,移植法或人造皮肤之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grafting or synthetic skin stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我不是科学家  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I-I'm not a scientist. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝上有多少工作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh-uh--how many crew aboard Big Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,大概猜个数  10个  20个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Estimate, guess. 10, 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:40.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,50个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}50?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,一百个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}100.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,坐下  他很快就出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have a seat. He'll be out shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用  不过谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no. Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家睡得好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How'd everyone sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,团聚有时会有些棘手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, reunions can be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉克斯  跟我说说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alex, tell me about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在外面的小研究项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}your little research project outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,听起来似乎没用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bit of a dud, by the sounds of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  看样子是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, yeah, looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉克斯  你妈妈的特别之处在于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The thing about your mother, Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是个修补匠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is she's a tinkerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,捣鼓卡钳还行  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Decent with a set of calipers, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:42.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,别指望她有多少远见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't expect much vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你认为你让我们陷入了僵局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you think you've stalemated us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们还有招  对吧  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we still have moves. Don't we, Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以踩刹车  减速缓行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can apply the brakes, slow it to a crawl,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,切断你们的动力  使你们的系统关闭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}choke out your power, and shut down your systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们的也会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的人知道如何在零度以下生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My crew know life below zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一同经历过很多崎岖的路程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've run a lot of rough miles together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车会分崩离析\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer will tear herself apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,当灯熄灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a hell of a test for a leader
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,食物供应不上时  这对领导者就是巨大的考验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when the lights go out and the food stops flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那位莱顿先生能撑多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long do you think this Mr. Layton will last?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会让你刮目相看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think he might surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我还真得会会他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess I'd better meet him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:34.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,有动静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下  蹲下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get down, get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  别碰它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait, don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能有毒  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, it could be poison, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,叫乘客服务部的人来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get Hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,乘客服务部  让下路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hospitality, make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,一群傻子  这是公报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fools, it's a communiqué.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,公报  让路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Communiqué, clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,让让\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,公报来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Communiqué coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德亲手写的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's in Wilford's own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,-露丝  露丝  -简直无可挑剔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Ruth. Ruth. - It's impeccable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生说我们一开始闹得不太愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Wilford suggests that we got off on the wrong foot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想见你  莱顿先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he would like to meet you, Mr. Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,他建议在正式囚犯交换时见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He suggests that that happens at a formal prisoner swap,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮换凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Melanie for Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们必须这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, we have to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会一枪崩了你的头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, might put a bullet in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,胡说  罗切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's nonsense, Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,别带着恶意揣测他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's not assume bad faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们困在了一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If we're stuck together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须开始相互交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we're gonna have to start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我现在得和他同步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I have to run two engines
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,运行两个火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in sync with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  但他怎么会交出梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, but why would he hand over Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在耍什么花招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:00.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,不像某些人  威尔福德先生很重视乘客服务部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Wilford, unlike some, values hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,尽管笑话我吧  罗切先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laugh at me all you like, Mr. Roche,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以肯定  凯文这个筹码比你们想得更重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm telling you that Kevin is a bigger chip than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧  如果这是公平交换\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, well, if it's an even exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那他就是想看着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then what he really wants is to look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们也看着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So we'll watch him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道他们大概有100个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We know that they number about 100
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且都很饥饿  这是我们的优势\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that they're hungry. That's good leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  去接梅兰妮回家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, let's bring Melanie home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们协议成交\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell 'em we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:38.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴  罗切  安妮还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to see you, Roche. How's Anne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,-她很好  先生  -那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She's great, sir. - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是...那是露丝·沃德尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And is that-- is that Ruth Wardell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,你换发型了吗  露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you changed your hair, Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir, I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想代表大家说一句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and might I say on behalf of everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,能再次见到您  我们不胜感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how truly grateful we are to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  办正事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, let's get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,想必这就是莱顿大王本人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, and here he is in the flesh--King Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有王权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No kings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在的雪国列车属于人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer belongs to the people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:11.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,那能麻烦你们的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then, could you please ask the people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,交出我的服务部部长吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to produce my head of Hospitality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,先立好规矩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rules first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有囚犯才能穿过无人区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one crosses the no man's land but the prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,任何突然的行为都会被视作挑衅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any sudden moves will be taken as a sign of aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,带他过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很好  威尔福德先生  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm fine, Mr. Wilford. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:33.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:41.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我走之前想见艾莉克斯  -下次吧  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I wanna see Alex before I go. - Next time, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会来找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:48.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  莱顿大王  就等你的准许了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, King Layton, with your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:04.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,开枪  开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take the shot! Take the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不要  住手  -别开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, stop! - Hold your fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,快告诉我这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟我走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll study it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:44.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来晚了七年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're seven years too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的火车怎么样了  莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's your train, Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,乘客有崩溃迹象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Passengers are starting to show cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,过往的分歧根深蒂固\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Old divides run deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝呢  威尔福德的下一步是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Big Alice? What's Wilford's next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,他自己都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think he knows yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他花了好几年筹划这次进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He planned this attack for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-现在只能即兴而为  -他为什么会交出你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Now he's improvising. - Why he turned you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好研究我们这边吗  -是研究你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To study our side? - To study you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他要冲你来了  莱顿  别搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's coming for you, Layton. Make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:33.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你女儿还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your daughter okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,她很无情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,困惑不已  她还恨我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's confused, and she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,青少年都这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So she's a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在外面待了很久  去看看医生吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were out there a long time. We should get you to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不了  去火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, to the Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得去找本和哈维谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need to talk to Ben and Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,借过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,他说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我得见昨晚被袭击的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I need to see the woman who was assaulted last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  但她不想见司闸员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, she don't wanna see no Brakeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,那幸好莱顿让我做了列车警探了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, it's a good thing Layton made me train detective then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,后退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, back it up, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,-后退  -放开  别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Back up! - Get off! Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,她和你们一同并肩作战  打什么打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She fought alongside you for Christ's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,离开我的走廊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now get out of my doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,-快走  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Get! - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever it's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定你是否能有更多进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know if you're gonna get much further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱茨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:34.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,贝丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你能告诉我发生了什么吗  -他们砍断了她的手指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can you tell me what happened? - They cut off her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没看见脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I--I didn't see faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:48.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们用袋子罩住了我的头  然后一拥而上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They put a bag over my head and piled on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,她之前在茶室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was up by the Tea Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们用了什么武器吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know what weapon they used on your fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,-可能是斧头  -天呐  这鬼地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Axe maybe. - Jesus Christ, this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我能走了吗  -这是给车尾的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Can I go? - It's a message to the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们袭击手  让她以后无法工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They went at the hands so she can't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想回到列车后方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want back downtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,前方容不下我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no place for us up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我是想帮你  莱茨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I'm trying to help you, Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,为时已晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:17.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我取样了一点雪  结果发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took a sample of the snow, and it turns out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:20.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,-里面含有硫酸铵  -你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- there's ammonium sulfate in it. - How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得海德伍德夫妇吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember the Headwoods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们活下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, they survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在那建立了一个生物实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have a whole wet lab over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在研究组织重生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're studying tissue regeneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,对了  这个伤口在他们最初治疗时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That, by the way, was third-degree frostbite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,是三级冻伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when they first treated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在几乎完全愈合了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's almost completely healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  硫酸铵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Back up-- ammonium sulfate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:33.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,在雪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,火山岩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Volcanic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想是CW7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it was CW7.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得它在大气中变性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it denatured in the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,-现在飘下来了  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- and now it's coming down. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你为什么会这么想  -因为下雪了  哈维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Why would you think that? - 'Cause it was snowing, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面有情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something's happening out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,有东西在变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something's changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果CW7飘下来了  如果的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If the CW7's falling--if--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要知道有多久了  得搞清楚飘下来的速率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we need to know for how long. We need to find out the rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,得搞清楚海拔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to find out the altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm glad you're back aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们行动吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get on this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,-大家需要听到一些好消息  -好的  老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Train could use some good news. - Yes, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来给您汇报  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here to give my report, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,进来  进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你让我好生担心  小伙子  -我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You had me worried, son. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  但是  请放心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm very sorry, but, rest assured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们对我挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they treated me fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你希望水多热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How hot do you want the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:54.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,给我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定累坏了  你值得好好泡个澡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You must be exhausted. You've earned a good soak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,您真慷慨  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, that's very generous, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯文  别推拖了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kevin, let me do this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以一边搓澡一边告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can scrub while you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在那的所见所闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all about what you saw up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:10.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的机械运转似乎一切正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they seem to be rolling fine mechanically,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,但社会方面一团乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but socially they're in shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,忽视规章制度  漠视命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Protocol is ignored, orders open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:20.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们似乎已经没有阶级了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't think they even have classes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,那莱顿呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他就是随机应变吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Winging it, as far as I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不让乘客服务部参与关键决策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He keeps Hospitality out of key decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw that with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们都不知道自己的归属了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People don't know where they belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:35.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知如何生存\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在交界处看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We saw at the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有指挥链  大家都疑心重重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No chain of command, everyone second-guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,混乱不堪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Totally untangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:52.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你透露了我们的什么信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what did you reveal about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,只说了一切正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only that all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们给你吃东西了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did they feed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们给了我鸡肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, they offered me chicken,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:17.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  所以我吃了几口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but...so, yes, I had a few bites,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那是午餐时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but, uh, you know, it was lunchtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,感觉应该吃一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so it seemed appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你先出去  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need the room, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I can get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不  留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no, no, no. Stay, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你让他们知道了我们在挨饿  凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You showed 'em we were hungry, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是个秘密  是我们的弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a secret. It's a vulnerability.
