Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:39.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了取胜  我们总有一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We gotta engage with him at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.43,0:31:40.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,要和他交手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}right, for the mission to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:43.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,露丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ruth.
