Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,绝不能接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's a nonstarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.51,0:32:57.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是和那个样本有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It has something to do with that sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.52,0:32:59.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道她没和我说实话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I knew she wasn't being straight with me.
