Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.24,0:34:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, I need a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.41,0:34:01.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,警探  你好像有点焦躁不安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Detective, you seem a little wound up.
